1: Scrape the data from the website/Sql database. Here we are using Amazon/Flipkart. We will particularly scrape the reviews of the different products. This step is called extraction.

2: The we will perform the tranformation of data and store it in native database. 
3: Then we will load the data in the vectordb and nosql.

After loading the data we will create the chatbot using RAG/Agentic RAG which will solve the confusion of selecting the product.

